## Vortice.Windows 3.6.2 DXGI Desktop Duplication API 조사 결과

DLL 디컴파일(ilspycmd)과 GitHub 소스 확인을 통해 얻은 **실제 타입 정보**입니다.

---

### 1. IDXGIAdapter.EnumOutputs() 시그니처

```csharp
// Vortice.DXGI.IDXGIAdapter
public Result EnumOutputs(uint output, out IDXGIOutput outputOut)
```

- 첫 번째 인자 `output`은 **`uint`** (인덱스)
- 반환값은 `Result` (HRESULT 래핑), `out`으로 `IDXGIOutput` 반환
- `GetOutput(int index)` 같은 편의 메서드는 3.6.2에 **없음**
- Factory에서 어댑터 열거: `IDXGIFactory1.EnumAdapters1(uint adapter, out IDXGIAdapter1 adapterOut)`

---

### 2. IDXGIOutput.Description / DesktopCoordinates

```csharp
// IDXGIOutput.Description 속성
public OutputDescription Description { get; }  // 캐시됨 (Nullable 내부)

// OutputDescription 구조체 주요 필드
public struct OutputDescription
{
    public string DeviceName;
    public RawRect DesktopCoordinates;   // <-- 핵심
    public RawBool AttachedToDesktop;
    public ModeRotation Rotation;
    public nint Monitor;                 // HMONITOR
}
```

**RawRect 구조체** (`Vortice` 네임스페이스, `Vortice.DirectX` 어셈블리):
```csharp
[StructLayout(LayoutKind.Sequential, Pack = 4)]
public readonly record struct RawRect
{
    public readonly int Left;
    public readonly int Top;
    public readonly int Right;
    public readonly int Bottom;

    public RawRect(int left, int top, int right, int bottom);

    // 암시적 변환: RawRect <-> System.Drawing.Rectangle
    // 암시적 변환: RawRect <-> Vortice.Mathematics.RectI
}
```

**DesktopCoordinates 접근 방법:**
```csharp
var bounds = output1.Description.DesktopCoordinates;
int width = bounds.Right - bounds.Left;    // int
int height = bounds.Bottom - bounds.Top;   // int
```

---

### 3. MappedSubresource / DataPointer 타입

```csharp
[StructLayout(LayoutKind.Sequential)]
public struct MappedSubresource
{
    public nint DataPointer;     // nint (= IntPtr), long 아님
    public uint RowPitch;        // uint
    public uint DepthPitch;      // uint

    // 편의 메서드
    public Span<byte> AsSpan(int length);
    public Span<T> AsSpan<T>(int length) where T : unmanaged;
    public Span<T> AsSpan<T>(ID3D11Texture2D resource, uint mipSlice, uint arraySlice) where T : unmanaged;
}
```

**핵심:** `DataPointer`는 **`nint`** (= `IntPtr`) 타입. `long`이 아님.

**Map 메서드 시그니처 (ID3D11DeviceContext):**
```csharp
// 간편 버전 (CheckError 자동)
public MappedSubresource Map(ID3D11Resource resource, uint subresource, 
    MapMode mode = MapMode.Read, MapFlags flags = MapFlags.None);

// Result 반환 버전
public Result Map(ID3D11Resource resource, uint subresource, 
    MapMode mapType, MapFlags mapFlags, out MappedSubresource mappedResource);

// 제네릭 Span 반환 버전
public Span<T> Map<T>(ID3D11Texture2D resource, uint mipSlice, uint arraySlice, 
    MapMode mode = MapMode.Read, MapFlags flags = MapFlags.None) where T : unmanaged;
```

---

### 4. D3D11.D3D11CreateDevice 사용법

`Vortice.Direct3D11.D3D11` 정적 클래스에 **9개 오버로드**가 있음. 주요 시그니처:

```csharp
// 1) 가장 간단 - device만 반환
public static ID3D11Device D3D11CreateDevice(
    DriverType driverType, 
    DeviceCreationFlags flags, 
    params FeatureLevel[] featureLevels);

// 2) adapter 지정, device만 out
public static Result D3D11CreateDevice(
    IDXGIAdapter? adapter, 
    DriverType driverType, 
    DeviceCreationFlags flags, 
    FeatureLevel[]? featureLevels, 
    out ID3D11Device? device);

// 3) adapter + device + featureLevel out
public static Result D3D11CreateDevice(
    IDXGIAdapter? adapter, 
    DriverType driverType, 
    DeviceCreationFlags flags, 
    FeatureLevel[]? featureLevels, 
    out ID3D11Device? device, 
    out FeatureLevel featureLevel);

// 4) adapter + device + context out (가장 많이 사용)
public static Result D3D11CreateDevice(
    IDXGIAdapter? adapter, 
    DriverType driverType, 
    DeviceCreationFlags flags, 
    FeatureLevel[] featureLevels, 
    out ID3D11Device device, 
    out ID3D11DeviceContext immediateContext);

// 5) adapter + device + featureLevel + context out (풀 시그니처)
public static Result D3D11CreateDevice(
    IDXGIAdapter? adapter, 
    DriverType driverType, 
    DeviceCreationFlags flags, 
    FeatureLevel[] featureLevels, 
    out ID3D11Device device, 
    out FeatureLevel featureLevel, 
    out ID3D11DeviceContext immediateContext);

// 6) nint 어댑터 포인터 버전도 있음 (nint adapterPtr 사용)
```

**주의:** `adapter`를 지정할 때는 `DriverType.Unknown` 사용. `null`일 때만 `DriverType.Hardware`.

---

### 5. Texture2DDescription Width/Height 타입

```csharp
public struct Texture2DDescription
{
    public uint Width;                    // uint (int 아님)
    public uint Height;                   // uint (int 아님)
    public uint MipLevels;                // uint
    public uint ArraySize;                // uint
    public Format Format;                 // Vortice.DXGI.Format
    public SampleDescription SampleDescription;
    public ResourceUsage Usage;
    public BindFlags BindFlags;
    public CpuAccessFlags CPUAccessFlags;
    public ResourceOptionFlags MiscFlags; // 3.6.2에서 MiscFlags (OptionFlags 아님)
}
```

**생성자:**
```csharp
public Texture2DDescription(
    Format format, uint width, uint height,
    uint arraySize = 1, uint mipLevels = 0,
    BindFlags bindFlags = BindFlags.ShaderResource,
    ResourceUsage usage = ResourceUsage.Default,
    CpuAccessFlags cpuAccessFlags = CpuAccessFlags.None,
    uint sampleCount = 1, uint sampleQuality = 0,
    ResourceOptionFlags miscFlags = ResourceOptionFlags.None);
```

**핵심:** Width와 Height는 **`uint`**. `RawRect`의 Left/Top/Right/Bottom은 `int`이므로, 변환 시 **캐스팅 필요**:
```csharp
Width = (uint)(bounds.Right - bounds.Left),
Height = (uint)(bounds.Bottom - bounds.Top),
```

---

### 3.6.2 기준 Desktop Duplication 전체 코드 예시

```csharp
using Vortice.DXGI;
using Vortice.Direct3D;
using Vortice.Direct3D11;
using SharpGen.Runtime;

// 1. DXGI Factory 생성
using var factory = DXGI.CreateDXGIFactory1<IDXGIFactory1>();

// 2. 어댑터/출력 열거 (GetAdapter 편의 메서드 없음, EnumAdapters1 사용)
factory.EnumAdapters1(0, out var adapter);
adapter.EnumOutputs(0, out var output);
using var output1 = output.QueryInterface<IDXGIOutput1>();

// 3. D3D11 디바이스 생성
var featureLevels = new[] { FeatureLevel.Level_11_0, FeatureLevel.Level_10_1 };
D3D11.D3D11CreateDevice(adapter, DriverType.Unknown, DeviceCreationFlags.None, featureLevels, out var device);

// 4. 출력 해상도 확인
var bounds = output1.Description.DesktopCoordinates;
uint width = (uint)(bounds.Right - bounds.Left);
uint height = (uint)(bounds.Bottom - bounds.Top);

// 5. Staging 텍스처 생성 (CPU 읽기용)
var textureDesc = new Texture2DDescription
{
    CPUAccessFlags = CpuAccessFlags.Read,
    BindFlags = BindFlags.None,
    Format = Format.B8G8R8A8_UNorm,
    Width = width,          // uint
    Height = height,        // uint
    MiscFlags = ResourceOptionFlags.None,  // 3.6.2: MiscFlags
    MipLevels = 1,
    ArraySize = 1,
    SampleDescription = new SampleDescription(1, 0),
    Usage = ResourceUsage.Staging
};
using var stagingTexture = device.CreateTexture2D(textureDesc);

// 6. Desktop Duplication
using var duplication = output1.DuplicateOutput(device);

// 7. 프레임 캡처
var result = duplication.AcquireNextFrame(500, out var frameInfo, out var desktopResource);
if (result.Success)
{
    using var srcTexture = desktopResource.QueryInterface<ID3D11Texture2D>();
    device.ImmediateContext.CopyResource(stagingTexture, srcTexture);
    // 주의: CopyResource(dst, src) - Vortice는 SharpDX와 인자 순서가 다름

